{"word":"G2014 - ἐπιφαίνω - epiphaínō - ep-ee-fah'-ee-no - Appear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiphaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-fah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Appear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிச்சம் தா, பிரசன்னமாகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to show to or upon; to bring to light"},{"paragraph":"2. to appear, become visible"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a>; to <i>shine upon</i>, that is, <i>become</i> (literally) <i>visible</i> or (figuratively) <i>known:</i> - appear, give light.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1718/1718\">G1718</a>, <a href=\"#/G2014/2014\">G2014</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015/2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016/2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316/5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318/5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319/5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320/5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321/5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322/5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324/5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325/5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326/5326\">G5326</a>"}]}